{"tid":2062416,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"非洲要求人權理事會 緊急討論種族歧視問題","createTime":"2020-06-13T06:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T06:22:33.000Z","uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1722fa9ffe65a13ab4fb0509d0e672711cbf0dcc","tid":2062416,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T06:19:06.000Z","msg":"楊明娟採訪<br />\n中央廣播電台<br />\n2020年6月13日 06:55<br />\n在非裔男子佛洛伊德(George Floyd)遭白人警察壓頸致死而引爆的全美示威仍持續之際，非洲國家12日要求聯合國人權理事會(U.N. Human Rights Council)緊急討論種族歧視問題。<br />\n<br />\n在54個非洲國家的一封聯合信函中，布吉納法索駐日內瓦聯合國的大使要求人權理事會，就種族歧視造成的違反人權，警察粗暴對待非裔人口，以及對要求停止不公的和平示威者使用暴力等問題，舉行「緊急辯論」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2067926\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2067926&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrqg2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=fa12a1a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2067926</a>"},{"pid":"d6c366e1c4759d27dba056e5ecd84d36bbab6d6a","tid":2062416,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T06:22:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ourworldindata.org/grapher/human-rights-scores?year=latest\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fourworldindata.org%2Fgrapher%2Fhuman-rights-scores%3Fyear%3Dlatest&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrqg2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=79dd1b3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://ourworldindata.org/grapher/human-rights-scores?year=latest</a><br />\n<br />\n人權地圖顯示非洲好有人權<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z5eU0Qq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz5eU0Qq.png&h=de15a759&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}